            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>7</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Total Tax Due"]</strong> - @Localizer["This is the total amount due for the bill. The Annual Secured Property Tax Bill has two payment stubs. The first installment is due November 1 "]
                @Localizer["and is delinquent December 10. If the first installment is not received or United States Postal Service (USPS) postmarked by December 10, a penalty will apply. "]
                @Localizer["The second installment is due February 1 and is delinquent April 10. If the second installment is not received or USPS postmarked on or before April 10, a 10 "]
                @Localizer["percent penalty and a $10.00 cost will be imposed. Taxpayers must be sure to include the payment stub with any type of payment and write their Assessor's "]
                @Localizer["Identification Number with the Year/Sequence Number on their check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>8</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Returned Check Charge"]</strong> – @Localizer["There is a $50.00 charge for any check returned by the bank."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>9</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Current Assessed Value"]</strong> - @Localizer["The Assessor’s valuation of the property after the adjustment."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>10</div>
            <p><strong>@Localizer["Prior Assessed Value"]</strong> - @Localizer["This is the Assessor’s valuation of the property prior to the recent transfer/new construction date."]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>11</div>
            <p><strong>@Localizer["Taxable Value"]</strong> - @Localizer["The current assessed value less the prior assessed value, if any."]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>12</div>
            <p><strong>@Localizer["Less Exemptions"]</strong> - @Localizer["Exemptions, if any, are deducted from the assessed value."]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>13</div>
            <p><strong>@Localizer["Net Taxable Value"]</strong> - @Localizer["The difference between the current value and exemptions."]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>14</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["2nd Installment Delinquency Date"]</strong> - @Localizer["If paying the bill in installments, the second installment must be received or United States Postal Service postmarked by "]
                @Localizer["this date, or a 10 percent penalty and a $10.00 cost will be imposed. "]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>15</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["2nd Installment Due"]</strong> - @Localizer["Amount of taxes due for the second installment. Taxpayers must be sure to include the payment stub with any type of payment and write "]
                @Localizer["their Assessor’s Identification Number with the Year/Sequence Number on their check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>16</div>
            <p>
                <strong>
                    @Localizer["Remit Amount"]
                </strong> - @Localizer["If payment is not made by the delinquency date, remit the amount stated here. Include the payment stub(s) with the payment and write the "]
                @Localizer["Assessor’s Identification Number and the Year/Sequence Number on the check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>17</div>
            <p>
                <strong>
                    @Localizer["Make Checks Payable"]
                </strong> - @Localizer["Make checks payable to the Los Angeles County Tax Collector and mail to this address. Include the payment stub(s) with the payment "]
                @Localizer["and write the Assessor’s Identification Number and the Year/Sequence Number on the check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>18</div>
            <p>
                <strong>
                    @Localizer["1st Installment Delinquency Date"]
                </strong> - @Localizer["If paying the bill in full, payment must be received or United States Postal Service (USPS) postmarked by this date. If "]
                @Localizer["paying in installments, the first installment must be received or USPS postmarked by this date, or a 10 percent penalty will be imposed."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>19</div>
            <p>
